# Study01 - Basic Preprocessing

## Overview
This study focuses on foundational concepts required for Deep Learning:
- Python basics
- NumPy operations
- Data visualization
- Dataset loading
- Image preprocessing

## Key Concepts
- Vector & Matrix operations
- Dot product (core of neural networks)
- Data visualization using matplotlib
- Dataset handling using pandas
- Preprocessing using torchvision

## Visual Outputs
Saved in /Visuals:
- line_plot.png
- scatter_plot.png
- iris_plot.png

## Conclusion
This study builds the base for ANN and Deep Learning by preparing data properly before training models.
